          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle your <strong>curry powder </strong>over your <strong>meat-free patty[ies]</strong> and pat it into both sides until evenly coated – this is your <strong>curried meat-free patty[ies]</strong></p>",
